scene.message:
Nanjo: Hearing talk of SEBEC{nl}
isn't exactly pleasant.{waitkey}{nl}
Never mind that, let's go{nl}
to the hospital.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Ah, the good old{nl}
haunted house!{waitkey}{clearbox}I used to play there a lot{nl}
as a kid, and my old{nl}
lady... er, mom would scold{waitkey}me for it...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: It was about a year{nl}
ago they tore down the empty{nl}
house and built the SEBEC{nl}
building there...{waitkey}{ret}

Student: You hear? There's{nl}
all these weird rumors about{nl}
the SEBEC building.{waitkey}{nl}
Like moans coming from it,{nl}
or red eyes peering from the{nl}
windows...{waitkey}{nl}
They built it where the{nl}
haunted house used to be -{nl}
folks say it's a curse.{waitkey}{ret}
